libtelepathy: libtelepathy (Telepathy Flexible Communications Framework)
libtelepathy: 
libtelepathy: The Telepathy project is building a unified framework for many 
libtelepathy: different kinds of real-time communications, such as instant messaging 
libtelepathy: (both one-to-one and in groups), voice calls and video calls.  It uses 
libtelepathy: the D-Bus messaging system to provide a simple interface for client 
libtelepathy: applications, allowing them to quickly take advantage of Telepathy's 
libtelepathy: benefits.
